---
---

<header class="hud">
  <div class="hud__score">Skor<span id="score">0</span></div>
  <div class="hud__score">Tur<span id="round">0/10</span></div>
  <div class="hud__score">Can<span id="lives">●●●</span></div>
  <div class="hud__score">Rekor<span id="best">0</span></div>
  <button id="restart" class="hud__btn" type="button">Yeniden başla</button>
</header>

<div class="board-wrap">
  <canvas id="board" width="540" height="420" aria-label="Cam Üfle atölyesi"></canvas>
  <div id="overlay" class="overlay" role="status" aria-live="polite">
    <div class="overlay__inner">
      <h2 id="overlay-title">Cam Üfle</h2>
      <p id="overlay-body">Hedef kürenin boyutuna ulaş, ama camı patlatma. <strong>Boşluk</strong> veya ekrana <strong>basılı tut</strong> → üfle. Bırakınca dondur. Çok büyük → patlar. Çok küçük → ham kalır.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<p class="cu-bars" aria-live="polite">
  <span class="cu-bar">Sıcaklık <span id="heat-bar" class="cu-bar__track"><span id="heat-fill" class="cu-bar__fill cu-bar__fill--heat"></span></span></span>
  <span class="cu-bar">Hedef <span id="target-label">—</span></span>
</p>
